      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "[reddit](https://www.reddit.com/r/AI_Agents/comments/1nxyz10/how_to_use_the_claude_agent_sdk_for_noncoding/)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Mental Model"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Think of deployment like "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ],
            "text": "setting up a restaurant"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ": serverless is like a food truck (pay when you operate, scales up/down), container is like a restaurant with a kitchen (you control the setup, can run 24/7), VPS is like a permanent building (dedicated space, you own everything). Security is like having a secure vault \u2014 you don't store valuables (API keys) in the kitchen (agent code), you keep them in a vault (proxy) and the kitchen gets authenticated access. Evaluation is like a taste test before opening to customers \u2014 you test the food (agent) before deploying."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Key Takeaways"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Three patterns: Serverless (AWS Lambda, Cloud Functions), Container (Docker, Kubernetes), VPS"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Serverless: burst workloads, auto-scaling, cost-efficient; Container: long-running, custom orchestration; VPS: 24/7 autonomy"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Secure deployment: place credentials outside agent boundary, use proxy that injects API keys"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "NEVER store API keys in code: use environment variables "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "code"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Production session store: Redis, PostgreSQL, or S3 (NOT InMemorySessionStore)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Docker: use Dockerfile with dependencies, ENV for API key, CMD to run service"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Kubernetes: deployment manifest with replicas, secrets for API keys, ports configured"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "VPS: dedicated VM, 24/7 autonomy, sessions persist across disconnects, full OS control"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Pre-deployment: create system prompt, agent loop, MCP tools, evaluate performance (key element)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Performance metrics: >90% success rate, <5s latency, graceful error handling"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Checklist: prompt \u2192 loop \u2192 MCP tools \u2192 evaluate \u2192 secure credentials \u2192 choose hosting \u2192 session store \u2192 monitoring"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "\"Anthropic's secure deployment guide recommends placing credentials outside the agent's boundary entirely\" \u2014 run a proxy that injects API keys so the agent never sees them directly."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}